            tage.</origDate></creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><facsimile><surface><graphic url="http://images.monasterium.net/pics/AT-WStLA/HA-U/WStLA-HA-Urkunden_00565_r.jpg"/></surface><surface><graphic url="http://images.monasterium.net/pics/AT-WStLA/HA-U/WStLA-HA-Urkunden_00565_v.jpg"/></surface></facsimile><text><body><div type="abstract" resp="lp"><p>
               <rs type="event" ref="#ev__QGW_II_I_565"><rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__johann_QGW_II_I_565">Jans <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__bartholomaeus_QGW_II_I_565"><add>prüder</add></roleName>
                        <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__jakob_stadtschreiber_QGW_II_I_217"><add>sun</add></roleName></rs> und <rs type="person" ref="#pe__bartholomaeus_QGW_II_I_565">Pertelme, die <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__johann_QGW_II_I_565">prüder</roleName>,<roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__jakob_stadtschreiber_QGW_II_I_217"><add>sun</add></roleName>
                           baide<rs type="person" ref="#pe__jakob_stadtschreiber_QGW_II_I_217">
                           Jacobs sun, des <roleName type="occ" corresp="#org__wien">statschreiber</roleName> ze Wienne</rs></rs></rs>, <triggerstring n="disp">beurkunden</triggerstring>, <rs type="event" ref="#ev__QGW_II_I_565_men_1">dass zwischen
                     ihnen und <rs type="person" ref="#pe__hermann_QGW_II_I_565">ihrem <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__johann_QGW_II_I_565">Vetter</roleName>
                        <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__bartholomaeus_QGW_II_I_565"><add>Vetter</add></roleName> Herman, <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__hermann_stadtschreiber_QGW_II_I_565"><add>sun</add>
                        </roleName><rs type="person" ref="#pe__heinrich_stadtschreiber_QGW_II_I_415">Hainreichs sun des <roleName type="occ" corresp="#org__wien">statschreiber</roleName></rs></rs>, ein Streit bestanden habe über
                     vierdhalb lb dn. geltes purchrechtes, welche ihre <rs type="person" ref="#pe__anna_QGW_II_I_565"><roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__johann_QGW_II_I_565">Muhme</roleName>
                        <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__bartholomaeus_QGW_II_I_565"><add>Muhme</add></roleName><roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__hermann_QGW_II_I_565"><add>Muhme</add></roleName>
                        <roleName type="title">junchvrow</roleName> Anna <roleName type="dead">selig</roleName>
                        <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__hermann_stadtschreiber_QGW_II_I_565"><add>tochter</add></roleName>,<rs type="person" ref="#pe__hermann_stadtschreiber_QGW_II_I_565"> Hermans tochter, des
                              <roleName type="occ" corresp="#org__wien">statschreiber</roleName></rs></rs>, auf <rs type="person" ref="#pe__martin_QGW_II_I_557">Merten haus,<roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__johann_von_schaffhausen_QGW_II_I_557"><add>sun</add></roleName><rs type="person" ref="#pe__johann_von_schaffhausen_QGW_II_I_557">
                           <roleName type="title">maister</roleName> Jansen sun <roleName type="dead">selig</roleName> von Schaefhausen</rs></rs>, gelegen in
                     der Wiltwericherstrasse ze Wienne, zenaechst Ulreichs haus des Pollen , gehabt
                     und auf welche Hermann alleinigen Erbanspruch erhoben hatte. Da die drei
                        Stadtschreiber<rs type="person" ref="#pe__jakob_stadtschreiber_QGW_II_I_217">
                        Jakob <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__hermann_stadtschreiber_QGW_II_I_565"><add>Bruder</add></roleName><roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__heinrich_stadtschreiber_QGW_II_I_415"><add>Bruder</add></roleName></rs>, <rs type="person" ref="#pe__heinrich_stadtschreiber_QGW_II_I_415">Heinrich <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__hermann_stadtschreiber_QGW_II_I_565"><add>Bruder</add></roleName><roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__jakob_stadtschreiber_QGW_II_I_217"><add>Bruder</add></roleName></rs> und <rs type="person" ref="#pe__hermann_stadtschreiber_QGW_II_I_565">Hermann <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__heinrich_stadtschreiber_QGW_II_I_415"><add>Bruder</add></roleName><roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__jakob_stadtschreiber_QGW_II_I_217"><add>Bruder</add></roleName></rs> Brüder waren, so brachten die
                     Streitenden ihre Sache vor den Rath, welcher dahin entschied, dass 14 sh. dn.
                     gelts an die Gebrüder Jans und Pertelme, 14 sh. dn. aber an ihren Vetter
                     Hermann fallen sollen</rs>. <rs type="fn" role="other"><triggerstring n="fn">Nach
                        dem Gebote</triggerstring>
                     <rs type="person" ref="#pe__rudolf_iv_herzog_von_oesterreich_QGW_II_I_769">des
                           <roleName type="title">Herzogs</roleName> Rudolf IV.</rs></rs>
                  <triggerstring n="disp">verkaufen</triggerstring> nunmehr Jans und Pertelme ihre 14 sh.
                  dn. gelts um 14 lb dn. <rs type="fn" role="recipient">dem vorgenannten <rs type="person" ref="#pe__martin_QGW_II_I_557">Merten, <rs type="person" ref="#pe__johann_von_schaffhausen_QGW_II_I_557">maister Jansen sun von
                           Schaefhausen</rs></rs>, und <rs type="person" ref="#pe__margarethe_QGW_II_I_571">seiner <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__martin_QGW_II_I_557">Hausfrau</roleName>
                     Marigreten</rs></rs>.</rs>
            </p></div><div type="seal"><p><rs type="event" ref="#ev__QGW_II_I_565"><rs type="fn" role="witness">Besiegelt mit
                     den Siegeln: 1. <rs type="person" ref="#pe__johann_QGW_II_I_565">des Jans</rs>,
                     2. <rs type="person" ref="#pe__ulrich_poll_QGW_II_I_1167"><roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Ulreichs des Pollen, <roleName type="occ" corresp="#org__wien">des rats der stat ze
                  Wienne</roleName></rs></rs>.</rs>
            </p></div><div type="lists"><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/placeList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/personList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/eventList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/orgList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/></div></body></text></TEI>